{"tid":464840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"56 Up英國記錄片 現今香港","createTime":"2017-11-11T02:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T02:48:34.000Z","uid":50353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"73b655ffaeeb9695fe7daf8576b7b3c364aa9dd9","tid":464840,"uid":50353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:48:34.000Z","msg":"從 1964 年開始記錄一群七歲的小孩，每隔七年訪問一次，一直到 2013 年他們 56 歲時結束拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n過去這個議題能夠隱性存在，是因為在成長的時代，看似人人都有往上爬的機會，但是當在停滯的時代，資源分配沒有重新調整，加上貨幣政策引發貧富差距擴大，階級問題就浮上檯面。<br />\n<br />\n現今的香港正正就係咁樣，睇完感覺到更絕望<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://technews.tw/2015/07/16/bbc-56-up/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2015%2F07%2F16%2Fbbc-56-up%2F&d=7VTm%2BqeeYZz6%2BOv%2BOZ%2BwxMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=18a8a695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://technews.tw/2015/07/16/bbc-56-up/</a>"}]}